  "instructions": [
    "Preheat broiler to high heat. ",
    "Line a baking dish with parchment paper or non-stick spray. ",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together eggs, mayonnaise, Dijon mustard, sour cream, lemon juice, garlic, black pepper, salt, cheddar cheese, chives, paprika, and cayenne pepper. ",
    "Stir in chopped fresh dill. ",
    "Pour the mixture into the prepared baking dish. ",
    "Drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle with bread crumbs. ",
    "Broil for 8-10 minutes, or until the topping is golden brown and the filling is set. ",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for a few minutes. ",
    "Garnish with additional fresh dill and serve hot. ",
    "Serve immediately, or refrigerate for up to 24 hours and serve chilled. "
  ],
